{"tid":657991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣側奶妹男友 「要看正面照的來這啦」","createTime":"2018-05-08T14:27:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T14:47:56.000Z","uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a5d5ce27b33d3ea56d4e8d7782134afc0227690b","tid":657991,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T14:27:12.000Z","msg":"台中網友近日直擊一名熱褲辣妹在對街買飲料，不知是不是衣服太大不合身，側面一望竟看到整個胸部曲線，引起熱烈討論，男友也出面力戰酸民，並控訴照片是租房時被房仲業者偷拍，「我們感到非常的氣憤」，另外許多網友也說想看熱褲辣妹正面照，他也PO出兩人合照，說「要看正面照的來這裡看一看啦」<br />\n<br />\n側奶妹的偷拍照PO網分享後引起熱烈討論，男友在《爆料公社》PO文，「今天要來上面發這篇文主因是因為我女朋友的正面照被po上網公審，我不懂外流的人心態是什麼，在我得知這張照片原來是我們昨天租房時被房仲業者偷拍，我們感到非常的氣憤！」<br />\n原來房仲業在被問了啞口無言後表示「因為我們公司規定完成合約就會拍客人照片存檔，目的是禁止業務之間搶客人，我也不知道怎麼會流出去，公司會嚴懲這位業務，我覺得您可以先針對網路上謾罵的人去備案」；對此男友也質問「不要跟我講公司規定，要拍為何不光明正大？幹嘛偷拍還上傳？偷拍沒有不對嗎？」<br />\n而許多網友看到側奶妹的背面照後，紛紛求正面照，側奶妹男友也霸氣貼出兩人合照，說「 要看正面照的來這裡看一看啦」，並強調他超級不爽房仲把偷拍照外流。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180508/640_89f24246aa8e301984f7074aff154845.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180508%2F640_89f24246aa8e301984f7074aff154845.jpg&h=ef217dce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180508/640_174f8a8e2248aab0f7412a90bf34c9d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180508%2F640_174f8a8e2248aab0f7412a90bf34c9d4.jpg&h=8d189b04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180508/640_88b714c6f73818f74bf785b12e38ad3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180508%2F640_88b714c6f73818f74bf785b12e38ad3f.jpg&h=675d4721&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以一戰"},{"pid":"526b2ae50f3e006ee417d2e77826ba10ae393b45","tid":657991,"uid":38904,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T14:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/17/022403_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F17%2F022403_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=be6da4d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6b7ec0efb01b3b23b315fdc9b1ddc304d079edf","tid":657991,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T14:32:42.000Z","msg":"男人"},{"pid":"d9af9b8fa98e310c7dc2ba5514d674244e1fd02d","tid":657991,"uid":137703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T14:36:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"466b3b84732f48e30116bec5093cf87f3088d405","tid":657991,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T14:36:58.000Z","msg":"不能只有我看到"},{"pid":"6c0b4cbcfe8c418e46cbcc8a5e5798592c567893","tid":657991,"uid":35451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T14:41:15.000Z","msg":"個髮型咩事"},{"pid":"e1496e0203ce975d9ea65a2cb18c670f44cf8ade","tid":657991,"uid":31094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T14:47:56.000Z","msg":"已射 thx"}]}